name: .21 SOLO WOMAN WALKS WITH BIRDS ON TEXEL ISLAND. photo w/artist enhancements. Lucky Lucy van Delft
description:
https://flic.kr/p/2mQK9pp - original photo

Took this pic on my own solo vacation (as per usual) & I guess the image of this woman spoke to me. Except it needed to be presented in it's more ideal form - hence I added lighting, highlights and birds. most of the enhancements are done using free gimp software as well an assortment of free custom brushes from brusheezy.
